        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我想公子卬与某情厚，未曾答报，怎好对敌？必须设下巧计，夺取吴城，方消"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "旧日之恨。哦，有了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，传众将进帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙套甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将进帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（少宫、任鄙、乌获同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "少宫",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "每日铠甲不离身，"
        },
        {
          "character": "任鄙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "任鄙威名谁不闻？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乌获",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "力分虎豹英雄胆，"
        },
        {
          "character": "少宫、任鄙、乌获",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要夺河西定五城！"
        },
        {
          "character": "少宫、任鄙、乌获",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺——"
        },
        {
          "character": "少宫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少宫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任鄙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "任鄙"
        },
        {
          "character": "乌获",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乌获。"
        },
        {
          "character": "少宫、任鄙、乌获",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "商君传唤，我等一同进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（少宫、任鄙、乌获同进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "少宫、任鄙、乌获",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅在上，众将参见！"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军少礼，请坐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "少宫、任鄙、乌获",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢座！传我等进帐，有何军务？"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今魏王差公子卬领兵五十万，前来应战。那公子卬，昔日与某交好深厚，情意"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未报，难以相敌，须用别计智取。若是撤兵，恐误国家大事，且前者之功，一"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "旦休矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "少宫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅，探马来报，那公子卬虽领十万之众，并无对敌之意，深知我国兵力强大，"
        },
        {
          "character": "少宫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "定要讲和。今听元帅之言，必要另寻别图；若是觌面相视，昔日情厚恩深，"
        },
        {
          "character": "少宫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如之奈何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "任鄙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "令尹之言差矣！食君之禄，效力朝廷，名扬千古，理所当然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乌获",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昔日乐羊取那中山，父子尚且不认，方能成功，说什么恩深情厚？如今各为其"
        },
        {
          "character": "乌获",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主，哪有以私废公之理？秦国兴霸，法令如山，元帅若是回兵，只恐三军不服"
        },
        {
          "character": "乌获",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！列公呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忆昔当年在魏邦，"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "穷愁潦倒甚栖遑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放我西行辅秦王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领兵十万有主张。"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "并非回军变主张。"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要取河西转还乡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪有忠良把君命抗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不取吴城不还乡！"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多蒙子卬仁义广"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他在魏邦把国掌"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两下兴兵各为主"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉王旨意领兵将"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叙论军机计往上"
        },
        {
          "character": "少宫",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅发笑为那桩？"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我心中只有好主张，"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可笑他魏兵尽丧亡！"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位将军，那公子卬前来，既然议和，我借此机会，计取吴城，易如反掌。"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，看文房四宝伺候！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。商鞅写信。旗牌暗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将此书信送到吴城，请公子卬亲启。"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（旗牌下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "少宫、任鄙、乌获",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅有何良策？"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此书一去，他若是见而无备，定然一鼓成功。子少听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "少宫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你带领一支人马，假称回军玉泉山。离此二十里，有一白雀山，前去安营扎"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寨，假言打围，附耳过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（商鞅耳语。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "少宫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（少宫下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乌获、任鄙听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "任鄙、乌获",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你二人带领三千人马，去至玉泉山后，暗扎营盘，山顶之上，设立黄旗一面，"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内安信炮，听候定夺，再来交令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任鄙、乌获",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（任鄙、乌获同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四下机关安排定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "商鞅",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "十万之众一夜倾。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
