    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "公子卬",
        "四上手",
        "报子",
        "旗牌",
        "龙贾"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套引龙贾同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙贾",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四下烟尘起，保主秉忠心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙贾",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "习就韬略盖世无，读尽战策学孙武。得展凌云安邦志，方显男儿大丈夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，龙贾。奉魏王之命镇守吴城，管理河西一带等处。可恨秦兵屡次犯界，前"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "者失去三城，每每交兵，不能取胜。也曾回朝搬兵，未见回报。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "令尹到！"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。四上手引公子卬同上，龙贾迎。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知元帅驾到，有失远迎，多多有罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军受尽风霜之苦，虽失三城，非将军之过。今秦兵压境而来，闻者丧胆，有"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何御敌之策？"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "食君之禄，当报君恩！怎奈贼兵狂大，我国兵微，难以布阵，故失三城，蒙主"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宽恩，粉身碎骨，理所当然！"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦兵势重，又有商君亲领大兵前来，威镇四方，闻名心寒。故奉主命，带兵十"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万，以防万一。我意欲与他讲和，免伤生灵，也好表吾主之仁义。不知此计安"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "否？"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁之言甚至是。但秦兵虎狼之辈，目无天子，意欲并吞列国，要自称为帝，"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂容我国讲和修好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军哪里知道，昔日商君在魏，是我待他情厚，荐过我主几次，吾主不用，故"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "投秦国而去。此番前来，当以前情动之，若念故土根本，事当有成！"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启爷：秦营下书人求见，言商君所差，要见千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传他进帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下书人进帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。旗牌上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走马传书信，要见主谋人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下书人叩头！"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉何人所差？到此做甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉秦国元帅所差，前来下书。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呈上来"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（旗牌呈书。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下面伺候！"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（旗牌下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "商君有书到来，待吾一观。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公子卬看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“鞅始与公子相得甚欢，不异骨肉。今各奉其主，为国之福，何望治兵，自相"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鱼肉？鄙意欲与公子相约，各去兵车，释甲胄以衣冠之会，于玉泉山相见，乐"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "欲修好，罢两国干戈，免人民涂炭。千秋之后，称我二人之处，同于管、鲍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公子如若俯允，幸示其期。”呀！不忘故土旧交，真乃慷慨之人！正合我意，"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃吾主洪福。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，传下书人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传下书人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（旗牌上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回营拜复商君，多承商君美意，决无二心，改日相会玉泉山，自当面谢，下面"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领赏！"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢元帅！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（旗牌下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦国逆理乱常。千岁此番赴会，若有奸诈，如之奈何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军不必细思量，"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他人未必有歹心肠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他感恩图报罢兵疆场！"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子卬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掩门！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公子卬暗下。龙贾、四龙套、四上手同下。）"
        }
      ],
